{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"So for the past year and a half,"},{"time":2000,"text":"my team at Push Pop Press"},{"time":4000,"text":"and Charlie Melcher and Melcher Media"},{"time":6000,"text":"have been working on creating"},{"time":8000,"text":"the first feature-length interactive book."},{"time":10000,"text":"It's called \"Our Choice\""},{"time":12000,"text":"and the author is Al Gore."},{"time":14000,"text":"It's the sequel to \"An Inconvenient Truth,\""},{"time":16000,"text":"and it explores all the solutions"},{"time":18000,"text":"that will solve the climate crisis."}]},{"cues":[{"time":20000,"text":"The book starts like this. This is the cover."},{"time":24000,"text":"As the globe spins,"},{"time":26000,"text":"we can see our location,"},{"time":28000,"text":"and we can open the book"},{"time":31000,"text":"and swipe through the chapters"},{"time":33000,"text":"to browse the book."},{"time":36000,"text":"Or, we can scroll through the pages at the bottom."},{"time":40000,"text":"And if we wanted to zoom into a page,"},{"time":42000,"text":"we can just open it up."},{"time":44000,"text":"And anything you see in the book,"},{"time":46000,"text":"you can pick up with two fingers"},{"time":48000,"text":"and lift off the page"},{"time":50000,"text":"and open up."},{"time":52000,"text":"And if you want to go back"},{"time":54000,"text":"and read the book again,"},{"time":56000,"text":"you just fold it back up and put it back on the page."},{"time":60000,"text":"And so this works the same way; you pick it up and pop it open."}]},{"cues":[{"time":63000,"text":"(Audio) Al Gore: I consider myself"},{"time":65000,"text":"among the majority"},{"time":67000,"text":"who look at windmills and feel"},{"time":69000,"text":"they're a beautiful addition to the landscape."}]},{"cues":[{"time":71000,"text":"Mike Matas: And so throughout the whole book,"},{"time":73000,"text":"Al Gore will walk you through and explain the photos."},{"time":76000,"text":"This photo, you can you can even see on an interactive map."},{"time":80000,"text":"Zoom into it and see where it was taken."},{"time":85000,"text":"And throughout the book,"},{"time":87000,"text":"there's over an hour of documentary footage"},{"time":89000,"text":"and interactive animations."},{"time":91000,"text":"So you can open this one."}]},{"cues":[{"time":94000,"text":"(Audio) AG: Most modern wind turbines consist of a large ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":97000,"text":"MM: It starts playing immediately."},{"time":99000,"text":"And while it's playing, we can pinch and peak back at the page,"},{"time":102000,"text":"and the movie keeps playing."},{"time":104000,"text":"Or we can zoom out to the table of contents,"},{"time":107000,"text":"and the video keeps playing."},{"time":112000,"text":"But one of the coolest things in this book"},{"time":114000,"text":"are the interactive infographics."},{"time":116000,"text":"This one shows the wind potential"},{"time":118000,"text":"all around the United States."},{"time":120000,"text":"But instead of just showing us the information,"},{"time":123000,"text":"we can take our finger and explore,"},{"time":126000,"text":"and see, state by state,"},{"time":128000,"text":"exactly how much wind potential there is."},{"time":130000,"text":"We can do the same for geothermal energy"},{"time":135000,"text":"and solar power."}]},{"cues":[{"time":143000,"text":"This is one of my favorites."},{"time":145000,"text":"So this shows ..."},{"time":150000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":154000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":156000,"text":"When the wind is blowing,"},{"time":158000,"text":"any excess energy coming from the windmill"},{"time":161000,"text":"is diverted into the battery."},{"time":163000,"text":"And as the wind starts dying down,"},{"time":165000,"text":"any excess energy will be diverted back into the house --"},{"time":167000,"text":"the lights never go out."},{"time":173000,"text":"And this whole book, it doesn't just run on the iPad."},{"time":176000,"text":"It also runs on the iPhone."},{"time":179000,"text":"And so you can start reading on your iPad in your living room"},{"time":181000,"text":"and then pick up where you left off on the iPhone."},{"time":183000,"text":"And it works the exact same way."},{"time":185000,"text":"You can pinch into any page."},{"time":187000,"text":"Open it up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":203000,"text":"So that's Push Pop Press' first title,"},{"time":205000,"text":"Al Gore's \"Our Choice.\""},{"time":207000,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":209000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":217000,"text":"Chris Anderson: That's spectacular."},{"time":220000,"text":"Do you want to be a publisher,"},{"time":222000,"text":"a technology licenser?"},{"time":224000,"text":"What is the business here?"},{"time":226000,"text":"Is this something that other people can do?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":228000,"text":"MM: Yeah, we're building a tool"},{"time":230000,"text":"that makes it really easy for publishers right now to build this content."},{"time":233000,"text":"So Melcher Media's team, who's on the East coast --"},{"time":235000,"text":"and we're on the West coast, building the software --"},{"time":238000,"text":"takes our tool"},{"time":240000,"text":"and, every day, drags in images and text."}]},{"cues":[{"time":243000,"text":"CA: So you want to license this software to publishers"},{"time":246000,"text":"to make books as beautiful as that? (MM: Yes.)"},{"time":248000,"text":"All right. Mike, thanks so much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":250000,"text":"MM: Thank you. (CA: Good luck.)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":252000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}